---
author: kewiha
---
Put @oatmeal, rolled/quick oats{0.33%cup} in a #bowl, microwave safe.

Add @cinnamon, ground{0.67%teaspoon} and mix thoroughly.

Add @raisins{0.33%cup}.

Add @water{0.67%cup}.

Microwave on high (i.e. default) for ~microwave1{75%seconds}

Stir thoroughly, then microwave on high (i.e. default) for ~microwave2{90%seconds}
